-- Bharat Sanchar to Order $3.5 Billion of Network Gear, Economic Times Says
-- B y   P r a t i k   P a r i j a
-- 2010-10-28T01:41:09Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-10-28/bharat-sanchar-to-issue-3-5-billion-equipment-tender-economic-times-says.html
Bharat Sanchar Nigam Ltd. plans to
issue a $3.5 billion tender to buy telecommunications equipment
and a third of which will be reserved for state-run ITI Ltd.,
the Economic Times reported, citing an unidentified official who
is aware of the development.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Pratik Parija in New Delhi at 
 pparija@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Margo Towie at 
 mtowie@bloomberg.net  